"67:3:18" : {s: 67, a: 3, w: 18, r: "فطر", t: "فُطُورٍۢ", l: "فُطُور", lc: 1, tl: "fuṭūrin", lb: "সকালের খাবার, চিড়, ভাঙ্গন, ত্রুটি,",e: "flaw", b: "ত্রুটি", i: "teratur/seimbang", f: 1, rm: "to create out of nothing, cleave/split/crack/break, be broken into pieces, cleave asunder, begin to create. fitrat - natural disposition or constitution with which a child is created. The faculty of knowing God and capability of accepting the religion of truth, religion. fatir  -creator, one of the names of Allah. futur - crack/flaw. munfatirun - split one, cloven one, one rent asunder.", ag: "أسم نكرة", eg: "Noun Indefinite state", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "INDEF", qual: "GEN", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "", mood: "", lu: "فَطَرَ،فَاطِرُ،مُنفَطِرٌۢ"},
