"67:4:8" : {s: 67, a: 4, w: 8, r: "خسا", t: "خَاسِئًۭا", l: "خَاسِئ", lc: 3, tl: "khāsi-an", lb: "ক্ষতিগ্রস্ত",e: "humbled", b: "ব্যর্থ হয়ে", i: "membingungkan", f: 1, rm: "To drive away (a dog), to be dazzled/confused and dim (said of the sight), to be driven away/repelled, throw stones at another.", ag: "أسم فاعل", eg: "Noun Active participle", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACT_PCPL", qual: "ACC", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "", mood: "", lu: ""},
"67:4:9" : {s: 67, a: 4, w: 9, r: "", t: "وَهُوَ", l: "", lc: 3307, tl: "wahuwa", lb: "",e: "while it", b: "এবং তা (হবে)", i: "dan ia", f: 171, rm: "", ag: "واو الحال وضمير ", eg: "Circumstantial wa and Personal pronoun ", tag: "PRON", pos: "PRON", att: "", qual: "", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: ""},
"67:4:10" : {s: 67, a: 4, w: 10, r: "حسر", t: "حَسِيرٌۭ", l: "حَسِير", lc: 1, tl: "ḥasīrun", lb: "ক্লান্ত, শ্রান্ত, দুঃখিত, বিষন্ন",e: "(is) fatigued", b: "ক্লান্তশ্রান্ত", i: "lemah", f: 1, rm: "To get tired/fatigued/jaded, fall short. To remove/put off/take off/strip off something, to peel, to sweep, to sink and disappear, to be low or retired, to be weary, to be dim or dull, express grief or sorrow or regret, to despise someone, to annoy or vex someone, drive someone away, cause someone to experience or fall into grief or regret, to moult or shed feathers (birds), to fall or fall off due to fatigue, to uncover something, to be removed or cleared away.", ag: "أسم نكرة", eg: "Noun Indefinite state", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "INDEF", qual: "NOM", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "حَسِيرٌۭ"},
"67:5:1" : {s: 67, a: 5, w: 1, r: "", t: "وَلَقَدْ", l: "قَد", lc: 406, tl: "Walaqad", lb: "ইতিমধ্যে (জোর দিয়ে বলা)",e: "And certainly", b: "এবং নিশ্চয়", i: "dan sesungguhnya", f: 122, rm: "", ag: "واو استئنافية ولام التوكيد وحرف تحقيق ", eg: "Resumption wa and Emphatic lām and Certainty particle ", tag: "CERT", pos: "CERT", att: "", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "", num: "", mood: "", lu: ""},
"67:5:2" : {s: 67, a: 5, w: 2, r: "زين", t: "زَيَّنَّا", l: "زَيَّنَ", lc: 26, tl: "zayyannā", lb: "সাজানো",e: "We have beautified", b: "আমরা সাজিয়েছি", i: "Kami menghiasi", f: 4, rm: "To adorn, deck. Adorn, grace, honor [said of an action, quality, or saying]. Embellished, dressed, or trimmed it [relating to language]. Adorned [ex. The earth, or land, became adorned with or by its herbage], ornamented, decorated, decked, bedecked, garnished, embellished, beautified, or graced him/it. Of language it is said: It was embellished, dressed up, or trimmed. Of action it is said: It was embellished, dressed up; i.e. commended to a person by another man. A grace, a beauty, a comely quality, a physical/intellectual adornment, an honour or a credit, and anything that is the pride or glory of a person or a thing. A thing that does not disgrace or render unseemly a wise man in any of his states or conditions, either in the present world or in that which is to come. It [states] are of three kinds: Mental: Such as knowledge/science and good tenants. Bodily: Strength, tallness of stature, beauty of aspect. Extrinsic: Wealth, rank or station, dignity.", ag: "فعل ماض صيغة ٢ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Perfect 2nd form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(II)", deg: "1", gen: "", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "زَيَّنَ،زُيِّنَ،زِينَةُ"},
"67:5:3" : {s: 67, a: 5, w: 3, r: "سمو", t: "ٱلسَّمَآءَ", l: "سَمَآء", lc: 310, tl: "l-samāa", lb: "আকাশ, মহাকাশ, আমাদের উপরে সব কিছু",e: "the heaven", b: "আকাশকে", i: "langit", f: 13, rm: "", ag: "ال التعريف وأسم منصوب", eg: "Determiner al and Noun Accusative case", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "ACC", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "", mood: "", lu: "ٱسْمُ"},
"67:5:4" : {s: 67, a: 5, w: 4, r: "دنو", t: "ٱلدُّنْيَا", l: "دُّنْيَا", lc: 115, tl: "l-dun'yā", lb: "দুনিয়া",e: "nearest", b: "নিকটবর্তী", i: "dunia/yang dekat", f: 115, rm: "To be near, come near or low, let down, be akin to.  Danaa (prf. 3rd. p.m. sing.): He drew near. Yudniina (imp. 3rd. p.f. plu.): They should let down, draw lower. Daanin (act. pic. m. sing.): Near at hand; bending (so) low (as to be within easy reach to pluck). Adnaa (elative.): Nearest; worse; lower; best; more fit; more proper; more likely; more probable; nearer; near; less; fewer. Dunyaa: This world.", ag: "ال التعريف وصفة منصوب", eg: "Determiner al and Adjective Accusative case", tag: "ADJ", pos: "ADJ", att: "ACC", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "F", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "أَدْنَىٰٓ،دَنَا،دَانٍۢ،دَانِيَةٌۭ"},
"67:5:5" : {s: 67, a: 5, w: 5, r: "صبح", t: "بِمَصَٰبِيحَ", l: "مِصْبَاح", lc: 4, tl: "bimaṣābīḥa", lb: "বাতি",e: "with lamps", b: "প্রদীপরাশি দিয়ে", i: "dengan bintang-bintang", f: 2, rm: "to visit or greet in the morning. subhun/sabahun/isbaahun - the morning. misbaahun (pl. masaabih) - lamp. sabbah (vb. 2) - to come to, come upon, greet, drink in the morning. asbaha - to enter upon the time of the morning, appear, begin to do, to be, become, happen. musbih - one who does anything in or enters upon the morning.", ag: "باء الجر وأسم مجرور", eg: "Preposition bi and Noun Genitive case", tag: "N", pos: "N", att: "GEN", qual: "", deg: "", gen: "M", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَصْبَحَ،صَبَاحُ،مِصْبَاحٌ"},
"67:5:6" : {s: 67, a: 5, w: 6, r: "جعل", t: "وَجَعَلْنَٰهَا", l: "جَعَلَ", lc: 340, tl: "wajaʿalnāhā", lb: "বানানো, নিযুক্ত করা",e: "and We have made them", b: "এবং তা আমরা বানিয়েছি", i: "dan Kami menjadikannya", f: 3, rm: "He made a thing, he created/brought into being/existence. He made to be/become/constitute. He made to be in a altered state/condition. He pronounced a thing by a true judgement/decision/legal ordinance, his judgement. Described them as females, pronounced them to be females, He made known/plain, He exalted/ennobled/called/named (as in a nation) He inserted a thing into a thing (Ex: They put their fingers into their ears) He put into the heart/mind, He appointed/assigned/stipulated to give wages/pay/stipend. He set about/began/commenced/commenced/took to/betook himself to, doing such a thing;  He persisted,  a piece of rag with which a cooking pot is put down from the fire, short palm trees/shoots/offsets.", ag: "واو عطف وفعل ماض وضمير متصل وضمير متصل ", eg: "Conjunction wa and Verb Perfect and Pronoun suffix and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "", deg: "1", gen: "", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "جَعَلَ،جَعَلَا،جَاعِلٌۭ"},
